{"tid":1913724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"逾51%人認為鄧炳強投訴港台節目《頭條新聞》投訴合理","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T07:47:08.000Z","uid":185631,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"368cd9c96d8e4ba3b5877f64bdf6cd5de00b1a2b","tid":1913724,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFXUwOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFXUwOv.png&h=bc4efc98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1292&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=c9c632f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1292</a>"},{"pid":"f051a2ef4bb2af2a2a8140a58fc0998b026fcb55","tid":1913724,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"推，on9報<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b894a491a79f09e682fffec391f5c3991ae86d4","tid":1913724,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士去晒邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bb617bd32ab2a4514e3f942e5a203e8482adeb","tid":1913724,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"835490e04bb220122b0b2af0b430792ce34fe34e","tid":1913724,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b894a491a79f09e682fffec391f5c3991ae86d4","tid":1913724,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士去晒邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"出黎啊!"},{"pid":"c7eb3a757201f292340fce7bb71056dc5890fe2b","tid":1913724,"uid":254461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"gogogo"}]}